(776, 'Ssup', '', '74393', '', '', '05-2015', 0.00, '', 'Thailand', 'WATER GLYCERIN BUTYLENE GLYCOU CARBOMER POLYSORBATE 20/ PALMITOYL PENTAPEPTIDE-4 PALMITOYL HEXAPEPTIDE-12 NIACINAMIDE METHYLSILANOL MANNURONATE PROPYLENE GLYCOL DIPROPYLENE GLYCOL SECALE CEREALE (RYE) SEED EXTRACT CETEARYL ALCOHOL DICETYL PHOSPHATE/ CETETH-10 PHOSPHATE MEDICAGO SATIVA (ALFALFA) EXTRACT ETHOXYDIGLYCOL DICAPRYLYL CARBONATE ETHYLENE/ ACRYLIC ACID COPOLYMER POLYGLYCERYL-3 METHYLGLUCOSE DISTEARATE PAPAIN 12 HEXANEDIOL CAPRYLYL GLYCOU ALGIN HYDROLYZED OPUNTIA FICUS-INDICA FLOWER EXTRACT ALPHA-ARBUTIN OCTADECENEDIOIC ACID 1-METHYLHYDANTOIN-2-IMIDE ACETYL TYROSINE PEG-8/ TOCOPHEROU ASCORBYL PALMITATE/ ASCORBIC ACID/ CITRIC ACID CELLULOSE ACETATE BUTYRATE/ URSOLIC ACID/ CHITOSAN TOCOPHERYL ACETATE SCUTELLARIA BAICALENSIS ROOT EXTRACT ALOE BARBADENSIS LEAF JUICE BISABOLOL DIPOTASSIUM GLYCYRRHIZATE CAPRYLIC/ CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE ISONONYL ISONONANOATE DIMETHICONE ACRYLATES/ C10-30 ALKYL ACRYLATE CROSSPOLYMER XANTHAN GUM PHENOXYETHANOU METHYLPARABEN/ ETHYLPARABEN PROPYLPARABEN TRIETHANOLAMINE CI 77891/ SILICA/ ALUMINA DISODIUM EDTA BHT FRAGRANCE', '', '', '', 0, '', '', 'ลูบไล้เซรั่มให้ทั่วใบหน้าและลำคอ ก่อนการใช้ครีมบำรุงผิวหน้าสำหรับกลางวันและการคืนเป็นประจำทุกวัน', 'This concentrated serum helps to whiten your skin diminish dark spot and increase skin firmness and elasticity in 14 day. It is enriched with the following ingredients : -Triple Whitening Complex-a powerful combination of Alpha Arbutin Vitamin C and Vitamin B that eliminates dark spots freckles melasma. Renew Bright-effective yet gentle exfoliant made from natural fruit extracts to even out your skin tone and reveal brighter looking skin. Firming Booster-a powerful combination of Double Peptides and Rye Extract to enhance your skin elasticity. French Seaweed Extract-a skin softener and moisturizer that provides long-lasting hydration. ', 'เซรั่มบำรุงผิวหน้า ช่วยให้ผิวแลดูกระจ่างใส ฝ้า กระ จุดด่างดำ ดูลดเลือนลงและช่วยให้ผิวแลดูตึงก