เท่าที่ต้องการ', 'Apply a generous amount on your face and neck. Use in place of night time moisturizer or as the last step in your night time skin care regimen. Use as often as needed.', '', '', '', 39.30, 25.60, 30.00, '', 0.00, '', 12.50, 6.40, 14.30, '68850080751699', '6', 120.00, '', 20.00, '1', '11-1-6200039802', '', '', 148.60, 0.00, 0.00, '', 0.00, '1999-11-30', 0, '1999-11-30', 0, '1999-11-30', 0, 'N', 0, 0, '', '', 0, '', 0, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '00D283', '2021-09-28 15:27:11'),
