-aging benefits of retinol without irritating the skin. It also contains 5% Niacinamide to effectively improve skin’s luminosity and reduce the appearance of enlarged pores. 4D Hyaluron Plus, a combination of 3 different molecular sizes of hyaluronic acid and a lamellar structure hyaluronic acid (Hyalorepair®), increases the skin’s moisture instantly and locks it in to restore skin’s smoothness. No matter your age or lifestyle, this sleeping mask will help you wake up looking well-rested with a youthful glow. ', 'ทามาสก์ทั่วใบหน้าและลำคอเป็นขั้นตอนสุดท้ายก่อนนอนโดยไม่ต้องล้างออก สามารถใช้ได้บ่อยเท่าที่ต้องการ', 'Apply a generous amount on your face and neck and massage gently into the skin. Leave it on overnight. It can be used as often as needed.', '', '', '', 0.00, 0.00, 0.00, '', 0.00, '', 22.50, 7.50, 6.50, '38850080754736', '3', 150.00, '', 50.00, '1', '11-1-6500031057', '', '', 467.29, 0.00, 0.00, '', 0.00, '1970-01-01', 0, '1970-01-01', 0, '1970-01-01', 0, 'Y', 0, 0, '', '', 0, '', 0, '00d492', '2022-11-04 09:23:38', '00D283', '2023-03-30 15:30:05'),
